title: RPMTALKS
description:
RPM talks is by the petrolheads for the petrolheads. We are a team of automobile
enthusiasts that share a wild passion for vehicles and are looking forward to introduce you
all to the incredible world of automobiles. We at RPM talks would be indulging you with the
latest news, turbocharged entertainment, extravagant interviews with leaders in the
automobile world, automobile-related news from throughout the world and exclusive
coverage from the city of Nashik. Buckle yourself in for an epic ride through the world of
automobiles with us and hope you enjoy the journey!

If you have any car related news, scoops or a hunger for automobiles, a wish to join us or contribute, please
contact us at rpmtalks@gmail.com
